              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",

              "    }\n",
              "  </style>\n",
              "\n",
              "    <script>\n",
              "      const buttonEl =\n",
              "        document.querySelector('#df-ff129a80-b92e-4cc8-8a48-c17bf5367e63 button.colab-df-convert');\n",
              "      buttonEl.style.display =\n",
              "        google.colab.kernel.accessAllowed ? 'block' : 'none';\n",
              "\n",
              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-ff129a80-b92e-4cc8-8a48-c17bf5367e63');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "\n",
              "\n",
              "    </div>\n",
              "  </div>\n"
            ],

              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-b5dc31ae-79bd-428d-a585-27435bded9f6');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
              "\n",

              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-6256360d-ef4b-469f-9b7c-a0ff9fd341b1');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",

              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",

      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "##Hyper permater tuning using XGBClassifier RandomSearchCV\n",
        "- recall(1)-92% , precision(1)-89% and accuracy 89%."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "PQyeMnqvi-z9"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "param_grid_xgb = {\n",
        "    'n_estimators':[100,200,300,500],\n",
        "    'learning_rate':[0.01,0.05,0.1,0.2],\n",
        "    'max_depth':[2,3,4,5],\n",
        "    'min_child_weight':[1,2,3,4],\n",
        "    'subsample':[0.6,0.8,1.0],\n",
        "    'gamma' : [0,0.1,0.2,0.5],\n",
        "    'reg_alpha':[0,0.1,0.2,0.5],\n",
        "    'reg_lambda':[1,1.5,2,3]\n",
        "}\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "B7SOz27WimYp"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "random_search = RandomizedSearchCV(\n",
        "    estimator = model_xgb,\n",
        "    param_distributions = param_grid_xgb,\n",
        "    n_iter = 50,\n",
        "    cv = 5,\n",
        "    scoring='accuracy',\n",
        "    n_jobs= -1\n",
        ")\n",
        "random_search.fit(X_train_encode,y_train)\n",
        "print('Best params :',random_search.best_params_)\n",
        "print(random_search.best_score_ )\n"
      ],

        "# In my dataset there are no missing value so i will start my pipe direct encoder\n",
        "trf1 = ColumnTransformer([\n",
        "    ('ohe',OneHotEncoder(drop='first',handle_unknown ='ignore'),[1,2,6,8]),\n",
        "    ('oe',OrdinalEncoder(categories=[['Up','Flat','Down']]),[10])\n",
        "    ],remainder='passthrough')"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "UZ8wj_Svgzqx"

        "    reg_alpha =0.5,\n",

        "    min_child_weight=2,\n",
